  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297160/extras/b6c734f70d4b8010cc77d4a62229639c.avif?t=1741113215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297160/extras_big/b6c734f70d4b8010cc77d4a62229639c.avif?t=1741113215 width=800 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tired of waiting for matches to start? Craving a healthy dose of frustration? Then \"NoRush\" is the perfect game for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297160/extras/da9b48993485a212c6c825547f551aa7.poster.avif?t=1741113215\" width=576 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297160/extras/da9b48993485a212c6c825547f551aa7.webm?t=1741113215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297160/extras/da9b48993485a212c6c825547f551aa7.mp4?t=1741113215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience the thrill of the climb:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Navigate perilous obstacles:</strong> Leap over deadly spikes, dodge swinging hammers, and avoid crushing platforms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Test your limits:</strong> Push yourself to the edge as the difficulty ramps up with each level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reach the 300-meter summit:</strong> Prove your worth and conquer the tower (though the view from the top might not be worth the struggle).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297160/extras/3799d4dbf2d220187851bb7369669525.poster.avif?t=1741113215\" width=576 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297160/extras/3799d4dbf2d220187851bb7369669525.webm?t=1741113215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297160/extras/3799d4dbf2d220187851bb7369669525.mp4?t=1741113215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This isn't your typical platformer.</strong> Expect challenging gameplay, unexpected twists, and plenty of opportunities to scream in frustration (and maybe laugh a little).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Download now and embrace the challenge!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297160/extras/35cce02b0d080b00c1c3a9edadf38e56.avif?t=1741113215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297160/extras_big/35cce02b0d080b00c1c3a9edadf38e56.avif?t=1741113215 width=800 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
